OL,3,CConvicted rapist pleads guilty to
OL,4,C'devastating' #700,000 fraud
OL,6,FThe former owner of a Jersey
OL,7,Frestaurant has pleaded guilty to four
OL,8,Fcounts of fraud and forgery, totalling
OL,9,Fmore than #700,000.
OL,11,FGavin Roberts, 46, is currently
OL,12,Fserving a 15-year prison sentence for
OL,13,Fa series of offences, including rape.
OL,15,FHe ran the now-defunct Shinzo
OL,16,Frestaurant in St Aubin, which closed
OL,17,Fin 2022 after building up thousands of
OL,18,Fpounds of debt.
