OL,3,CConvicted rapist pleads guilty to
OL,4,C'devastating' #700,000 fraud
OL,6,FAt Jersey's Royal Court on Friday, he
OL,7,Fadmitted committing fraud and forgery
OL,8,Fbetween 2018 and 2022.
OL,10,FThe specialist financial crimes unit
OL,11,Fwithin the States of Jersey Police
OL,12,Finvestigated Roberts and says the
OL,13,Fimpact of his crimes has been
OL,14,F"devastating" for the people who were
OL,15,Ftargeted.
OL,17,FA spokesperson adds: "We commend their
OL,18,Fcourage in coming forward and their
OL,19,Fcooperation throughout the
OL,20,Finvestigation.
