OL,3,CConvicted rapist pleads guilty to
OL,4,C'devastating' #700,000 fraud
OL,6,F"This was a long and complex
OL,7,Finvestigation which has resulted in
OL,8,FRoberts admitting to deliberately
OL,9,Fdeceiving victims, all of whom
OL,10,Fsuffered not only financial hardship
OL,11,Fbut also emotional distress.
OL,13,F"Today's guilty plea is a step toward
OL,14,Fjustice, and we hope it brings some
OL,15,Fmeasure of closure to those affected."
OL,17,FRoberts will be sentenced for his
OL,18,Flatest crimes at Jersey's Royal Court
OL,19,Fon Thursday 25 September.
